The high commission in salons

You can choose low commission (only for new clients) or a monthly subscription without any commission, regardless of the volume of work! Take advantage of the 30-day free trial period, with no payments at all for working with your clients.

It’s difficult to find new clients

Acquiring new clients has never been so simple! All you need to do is complete a specialist profile that indicates the services/work that you offer and your prices. We’ll take care of everything when it comes to attracting new clients!

Beauty will save the World, and Glambook will save beauty!

